"title": "4903: time",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4903",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A creation of God which marks the duration of life and which is measured by changes in the created order. The flow of time is directed by God who appoints particular “times” within his unfolding purposes. Because human life is brief, time should be used properly, making the most of every opportunity.</p>\n<h2>Time as a creation of God</h2>\n<h3>Time began at creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:5\">GEN 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:7\">1CO 2:7</a></p>\n<h3>Time is marked by change in the created order</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:14\">GEN 1:14</a></strong> <em>The main divisions of time were based upon the phases of the sun and moon.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:19\">PSA 104:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:20\">JER 33:20</a></p>\n<h3>The timelessness of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:2\">PSA 90:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:2\">PSA 93:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:26\">PRO 8:22–8:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12\">HAB 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:2\">JHN 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h3>God's perception of time</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:8\">2PE 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:4\">PSA 90:4</a></p>\n<h2>Measurement of time</h2>\n<h3>Divisions of time</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:8\">GEN 1:8</a> <em>A day was marked by the regular cycle of evening and morning</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:14\">NUM 28:14</a> <em>Months were determined by the regular phases of the moon</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:7\">1KI 4:7</a> <em>The year consisted of twelve lunar months</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:9\">JHN 11:9</a> <em>An hour was one twelfth of the period of daylight.</em></p>\n<h3>Indefinite periods of time</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:22\">1SA 1:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:14\">JER 32:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:9\">LUK 20:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:28\">ACT 14:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:23\">ACT 18:23</a></p>\n<h2>Recurring times and seasons</h2>\n<h3>God's seasonal provision</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:14\">DEU 11:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:4\">LEV 26:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:12\">DEU 28:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:15-Ps145:16\">PSA 145:15–145:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:24\">JER 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></p>\n<h3>Appointed times for festivals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:4\">LEV 23:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:10\">EXO 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:15\">EXO 23:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:18\">EXO 34:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num9:2-Num9:3\">NUM 9:2–9:3</a></p>\n<h3>A right time for every activity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:1-Eccl3:8\">ECC 3:1–3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:11\">ECC 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:6\">ECC 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:7\">JER 8:7</a></p>\n<h3>Times of human life in God's hands</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:15\">PSA 31:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:16\">PSA 139:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:5\">JOB 14:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:21\">DAN 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a></p>\n<h2>Appointed times within God's unfolding purpose</h2>\n<h3>The time of fulfilment of promise</h3>\n<p>The time of Isaac's birth:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:2\">GEN 21:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:9\">ROM 9:9</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:20\">LUK 1:20</a> <em>the time of John the Baptist's birth</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:17\">ACT 7:17</a> <em>the time of Israel's possession of the land</em></p>\n<h3>The time of Israel's deliverance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:13\">PSA 102:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:3\">HAB 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:16\">HAB 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>The time of Jesus Christ's coming</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:2-Gal4:4\">GAL 4:2–4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:44\">LUK 19:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:6\">1TI 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:3\">TIT 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>The time of Jesus Christ's death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:23\">JHN 12:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:18\">MAT 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:4\">JHN 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:20\">JHN 8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:6\">ROM 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:11\">1PE 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>The time of Jesus Christ's return</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:36\">MAT 24:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:10\">EPH 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15\">1TI 6:15</a></p>\n<h3>The time of God's judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps75:2\">PSA 75:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:7-Ezek7:8\">EZK 7:7–7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:14\">EZK 24:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:2\">ZEP 2:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:29\">MAT 8:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:18\">REV 11:18</a></p>\n<h3>The appointed time of the end</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:19\">DAN 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:27\">DAN 11:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:29\">DAN 11:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32\">MRK 13:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:6-Acts1:7\">ACT 1:6–1:7</a></p>\n<h2>The time between Jesus Christ's first and second coming</h2>\n<h3>The time of salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:2</a></strong> <em>The time of salvation lies between the two comings of Jesus Christ.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:8\">ISA 49:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:13\">HEB 11:13</a></p>\n<h3>The end times</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17\">ACT 2:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2\">HEB 1:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:20\">1PE 1:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:18\">1JN 2:18</a></p>\n<h2>Proper use of time</h2>\n<h3>Recognising the brevity of human life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:12\">PSA 90:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:4-Ps39:6\">PSA 39:4–39:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:1\">PRO 27:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:14\">JAS 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Seeking God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:6\">ISA 55:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:6\">PSA 32:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:13\">PSA 69:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:7-Ps95:8\">PSA 95:7–95:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:1\">ECC 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:6-Eccl12:7\">ECC 12:6–12:7</a></p>\n<h3>Looking to eternal realities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:29-1Cor7:31\">1CO 7:29–7:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:6\">PSA 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:12\">ISA 56:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:11-Rom13:12\">ROM 13:11–13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:7-Jas5:9\">JAS 5:7–5:9</a></p>\n<h3>Making the most of opportunities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:5\">COL 4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:16\">EPH 5:16</a></p>",
